  <brief_title>Maintenance Therapy With Histamine Dihydrochloride and Interleukin-2 in Adult Acute Myeloid Leukemia (AML) Patients With Measurable Minimal Residual Disease (MRD)- a Non-interventional Study (NIS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Maintenance Therapy With Histamine Dihydrochloride and Interleukin-2 in Adult Acute Myeloid Leukemia (AML) Patients With Measurable Minimal Residual Disease (MRD)- a Non-interventional Study (NIS)</official_title>
